# The Bun Theory Typography & Nav

- Use `Comic Sans MS` (or the configured display-font fallback) for display text:
  headings, section titles, navbar brand text, navbar links, buttons, labels, and CTA copy.
- Keep body copy readable in the existing sans body font unless the user asks otherwise.
- Landing and admin navbars should feel like the same design system:
  larger desktop brand/logo treatment, rounded nav pills, and comparable text sizing.
- Do not shrink the landing-page brand mark or title on desktop; prioritize visibility.
- If a new navbar/header is added, match the sizing rhythm used in `customer-shell.tsx` and `app/admin/layout.tsx`.
